,(431,0,'CANCELLATION','{"legal":{"1":"<p style=\\"text-align:justify; margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt\\"><span style=\\"font-size:12px;\\"><strong>CANCELLATION OF ENTIRE GROUP</strong></span></p><ol start=\\"1\\" style=\\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\\"><li style=\\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-size:12px;\\">181 days or more prior to scheduled arrival initial deposit is not refundable, however additional damages will not be assessed.</span></li><li style=\\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-size:12px;\\">Between 180 - 91 days prior to scheduled arrival, 50% of the total net room revenue will be assessed. Minus rooms resold.</span></li><li style=\\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-size:12px;\\">Between 90- 31 days prior to scheduled arrival, 90% of the total net room revenue will be assessed. Minus rooms resold.</span></li><li style=\\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-size:12px;\\">Between 30 - 0 days prior to scheduled arrival, 100% of total net room revenue will be assessed. </span></li><li style=\\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-size:12px;\\">Cancellation assessments are due to Company at time of cancellation.</span><br><br></li></ol><ul><li style=\\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-size:12px;\\">Attrition will be based on the total number of room nights contracted, not on peak nights. Reduction of rooms on any of the Official Group Dates must apply equally for each date that is named as Official, in the previous clause of this contract. Failure to do so may be considered by the hotel to be a breach of contract, therefore causing the group to be subject to availability and re-quotation.</span></li><li style=\\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-size:12px;\\">Attrition and no shows will be charged as single or dou